## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of how culture influences health. Some sources may not be peer-reviewed, and the information is subject to the limitations of the data available up to October 2023. Additionally, cultural influences on health can vary widely across different regions and communities, which may not be fully captured in this report.

